chedulePublishDate":"","children":"/rest/api/content/2178416778/child","ancestors":"","draftVersion":""},"_links":{"self":"https://qubika.atlassian.net/wiki/rest/api/content/2178416778","tinyui":"/x/igDYgQ","editui":"/pages/resumedraft.action?draftId=2178416778","webui":"/spaces/BAN/overview","edituiv2":"/spaces/BAN/pages/edit-v2/2178416778"}},{"id":"2316959745","type":"page","ari":"ari:cloud:confluence:4e3a1a04-13f1-4674-95f6-44812aec1da3:page/2316959745","base64EncodedAri":"YXJpOmNsb3VkOmNvbmZsdWVuY2U6NGUzYTFhMDQtMTNmMS00Njc0LTk1ZjYtNDQ4MTJhZWMxZGEzOmNvbnRlbnQvMjMxNjk1OTc0NQ==","status":"current","title":"TMP","macroRenderedOutput":{},"extensions":{"position":887957284},"_expandable":{"container":"/rest/api/space/BAN","metadata":"","restrictions":"/rest/api/content/2316959745/restriction/byOperation","history":"/rest/api/content/2316959745/history","body":"","version":"","descendants":"/rest/api/content/2316959745/descendant","space":"/rest/api/space/BAN","childTypes":"","schedulePublishInfo":"","operations":"","schedulePublishDate":"","children":"/rest/api/content/2316959745/child","ancestors":"","draftVersion":""},"_links":{"self":"https://qubika.atlassian.net/wiki/rest/api/content/2316959745","tinyui":"/x/AQAaig","editui":"/pages/resumedraft.action?draftId=2316959745","webui":"/spaces/BAN/pages/2316959745/TMP","edituiv2":"/spaces/BAN/pages/edit-v2/2316959745"}}],"macroRenderedOutput":{},"body":{"storage":{"value":"<p>Gu&iacute;a para crear un servicio desde cero con Ruby on Rails. Se toma de base el procedimiento realizado para bancard-pix-service</p><ol start=\"1\"><li><p>Creaci&oacute;n del proyecto base con el comando rails new, utilizando las opciones acordes a la necesidad del proyecto.</p><ac:structured-macro ac:name=\"code\" ac:schema-version=\"1\" ac:macro-id=\"6ed20362-c81c-4454-8e07-7a4b28eacd23\"><ac:plain-text-body><![CDATA[rails new bancard-pix-service --database=mysql --api --skip-action-text --skip-action-mailbox --skip-active-storage]]></ac:plain-text-body></ac:structured-macro></li></ol><ac:structured-macro ac:name=\"info\" ac:schema-version=\"1\" ac:macro-id=\"a4fcf6bb-37ff-4d2a-b277-bf5cd31d2862\"><ac:rich-text-body><p>Es posible que se necesite instalar MySQL en el entorno local para poder inicializar el proyecto. En caso contrario, falla al momento de hacer bundle install.</p></ac:rich-text-body></ac:structured-macro><ol start=\"2\"><li><p>Agregar dockerizacion. Commit de referencia: <a href=\"https://github.com/bancardsa/bancard-pix-service/commit/c70447d6baedc6d1fce993f9d102fed2c0f7ed0b\" data-card-appearance=\"inline\">https://github.com/bancardsa/bancard-pix-service/commit/c70447d6baedc6d1fce993f9d102fed2c0f7ed0b</a> </p></li><li><p>Agregar gemas y dependencias:</p></li></ol><table data-table-width=\"760\" data-layout=\"default\" ac:local-id=\"0e6233bc-9a8a-43b4-92cb-85f135bac8fc\"><colgroup><col style=\"width: 165.0px;\" /><col style=\"width: 341.0px;\" /><col style=\"width: 253.0px;\" /></colgroup><tbody><tr><th><p><strong>Gema</strong></p></th><th><p><strong>Pasos</strong></p></th><th><p><strong>Commit de referencia</strong></p></th></tr><tr><td><p>Rubocop</p></td><td><ol start=\"1\"><li><p>Agregar la/s gema/s al Gemfile</p></li><li><p>Crear el archivo de configuraci&oacute;n .rubocop.yml</p></li></ol></td><td><p><a href=\"https://github.com/bancardsa/bancard-pix-service/commit/571853c29e70f471d90c2469fa3b908745c014fa\">Commit</a></p></td></tr><tr><td><p>RSpec</p></td><td><ol start=\"1\"><li><p>Agregar la gema rspec-rails</p></li><li><p>Instalar con el comando <code>rails generate rspec:install</code></p></li></ol></td><td><p><a href=\"https://github.com/bancardsa/bancard-pix-service/commit/cb3830193f0405947741c0af964a0d98dc73ee64\">Commit</a></p></td></tr><tr><td><p>Sidekiq</p></td><td><ol start=\"1\"><li><p>Agregar la gema</p></li><li><p>Agregar redis y el proceso sidekiq en el docker-compose.</p></li><li><p>Agregar la configuraci&oacute;n necesaria.</p></li></ol></td><td><p><a href=\"https://github.com/bancardsa/bancard-pix-service/commit/a4b52625283df1711ef32b663934e10561254148\">Commit</a></p></td></tr><tr><td><p>Brakeman</p></td><td><ol start=\"1\"><li><p>agregar la gema brakeman en el grupo develop</p></li></ol></td><td><p><a href=\"https://github.com/bancardsa/bancard-pix-service/commit/030f7d4b1ece71740a3fb2416e321673d908abc5\">Commit</a></p></td></tr><tr><td><p>Strong migrations</p></td><td><ol start=\"1\"><li><p>agregar gema al Gemfile</p></li><li><p>Correr el generador <code>rails generate strong_migrations:install</code></p></li></ol></td><td><p><a href=\"https://github.com/bancardsa/bancard-pix-service/commit/0d7a9d31006db680aa9d6791115de50020cb2039\">Commit</a></p></td></tr><tr><td><p>Sentry</p></td><td><ol start=\"1\"><li><p>Agregar gemas</p></li><li><p>Crear el initializer.</p></li><li><p>Agregar configuraciones correspondientes. </p></li></ol></td><td><p><a href=\"https://github.com/bancardsa/bancard-pix-service/commit/08b1c92918271933a00505f239d746ff2d5b1001\">Commit</a></p></td></tr><tr><td><p>Annotate</p></td><td><ol start=\"1\"><li><p>Agregar gema</p></li><li><p>Correr el generador <code>rails g annotate:install</code></p></li></ol></td><td><p><a href=\"https://github.com/bancardsa/bancard-pix-service/commit/a1ecd465da557043f2ea5031e024bcd8f87ced80\">Commit</a></p></td></tr><tr><td><p>Shoulda Matchers<br />Factory Bot<br />Faker<br />Jbuilder</p></td><td><p>Ver documentaci&oacute;n de cada gema y commit.</p></td><td><p><a href=\"https://github.com/bancardsa/bancard-pix-service/commit/4c51007975842e5c9ac84802f24a8e02ba3338f7\">Commit</a></p></td></tr></tbody></table><p />","representation":"storage","embeddedContent":[],"_expandable":{"content":"/rest/api/content/2843508752"}},"_expandable":{"editor":"","atlas_doc_format":"","view":"","export_view":"","styled_view":"","dynamic":"","editor2":"","anonymous_export_view":""}},"extensions":{"position":791369076},"_expandable":{"childTypes":"","container":"/rest/api/space/BAN","schedulePublishInfo":"","metadata":"","operations":"","schedulePublishDate":"","children":"/rest/api/content/2843508752/child","restrictions":"/rest/api/content/2843508752/restriction/byOperation","history":"/rest/api/content/2843508752/history","draftVersion":"","descendants":"/rest/api/content/2843508752/descendant","space":"/rest/api/space/BAN"},"_links":{"editui":"/pages/resumedraft.action?draftId=2843508752","webui":"/spaces/BAN/pages/2843508752/Creaci+n+de+un+nuevo+servicio+en+Ruby+on+Rails","edituiv2":"/spaces/BAN/pages/edit-v2/2843508752","context":"/wiki","self":"https://qubika.atlassian.net/wiki/rest/api/content/2843508752","tinyui":"/x/EIB8qQ","collection":"/rest/api/content","base":"https://qubika.atlassian.net/wiki"}}